==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[dens]]''', '''[[dent-]]''', ''tooth'', + agent suffix '''[[-ist]]''', from Latin suffix '''[[-ista]]''', from Greek '''[[-ista]]'''

===Noun===
'''dentist''', ''plural'' '''dentists'''

# A medical doctor who specializes in fixing people's teeth.

